data.title: China to deploy battery-swapping humanoid robots on Vietnam border
data.description: China's UBTech Robotics has secured a 264 million yuan (US$37 million) contract to deploy industrial-grade humanoid robots on border.
data.author: Kaif Shaikh
data.keywords: battery replacing robot, Border robots, Humanoid, Humanoid Robot, Industrial Robot, robot, Robotics, UBTech, UBTech Robotics, Walker S2
